      "title": "SLNSS members of SriLankan Airlines also to withdraw from service from noon",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sri Lankan Nidahas Sewaka Sangamaya (SLNSS) of the SriLankan airlines also decided to withdraw from services, in order to prevent responsible officials who are involved in the country's present crisis from leaving.",
        "Therefore, considering all aspects, the SLNSS has decided to withdraw from their duties from noon today and has also decided to stay away from passenger handling on the Silk Route/CIP."
      ],
